-- American Air expects 900 cancellations Thursday
-- 
-- Wed Apr 9, 2008 7:46pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/04/09/us-amr-cancellations-thursday-idUSN0940908620080409

 

 WASHINGTON  (Reuters) - AMR Corp's American Airlines, which canceled more than 1,000 flights on Wednesday to reinspect wiring on MD-80 aircraft, said it now expects 900 cancellations on Thursday. 

 The carrier still hopes to restore normal operations by Saturday, a senior executive said. (Reporting by  John Crawley )